Kim-ku3: Ia5-ho5-hoa ho2 khoan2-thai7 ban7-lui7, I e5 lin5-bin2 ti3-im3 I it-chhe3 sou2 cho3 e5. (Si-phian 145: 9)
U7 chit8 jit8 thinn chin ou, hong tit8-tit8 teh thau3, Gi7-sin3 tui3 hak8-hau7 chhut-lai5, seng-khu phainn7 chheh-pau, chhiu2 nih8 theh8 pian7-tong, khi2-thau5 chin toa7-pou7 teh kiann5, khoann3-tioh8 hong chin toa7 tit8-tit8 lai5, koh lui5 ia7 teh tan5, chin hoan5-lo2, sim-lai7 teh siunn7 un2-tang3 si7 beh loh8 sai-pak hou7, na7 beh tng2-khi3 kau3 i e5 chhu3 tioh8 ai3 koh chau2 chit8-tiam2 cheng-ku2, koh tioh8 ai3 keng-koe3 tek-pho7 chin choe7, lui5 ju2-tan5 ju2 toa7-siann, sih-na3 ia7 teh lai5. Gi7-sin3 kiann kau3 beh hau2 chhut-lai5, in-ui7 i bat thiann-kinn3 lang5 teh kong2 lui5 oe7 kong3-si2 lang5, tann beh chainn2-iunn7, oat8-thau5 khoann3 au7-bin7, long2 bo5 khoann3-kinn3 in e5 tong5-hak8-seng teh lai5, i2-keng kau3 tek-pho7 pinn chiu7 chhiann2 ti7 hia theng5 chhoan2.
Hut-jian5 lui5 kong3 chit8-e7 chin toa7 e7, Gi7-sin3 tioh8-kiann khi3 phak ti7 te7 nih8 chiu7 chhut-siann kio3 ma-ma, tui3 i e5 chheh-pau lam2 tiau5-le3, ti7 i sou2 lam2 e5 chheh te7-a2 lai7 i e5 chhiu2 u7 bong-tioh8 choa2 sou2 au2 e5 mih8, hit-si5 ti7 i e5 sim-lai7 chin kan-khou2, ah......ah, chit e5 si7 20 khou, goa2 ka7 sian-sinn moa5-phian3 kong2 goa2 teh kan-khou2, chiu7-si7 kiann-liau2 goa2 chit 20 khou khi3 hou7 sian-sinn chhiau tioh8, chiah e5 chinn5 si7 tong5-hak8 e5 chheh-chinn5 goa2 ka7 theh8-lai5, un2-tang3 i ti7 hia teh chhoe7 bo5; m7-chai u7 teh hau2 a2-bo5? Ti7 an2-ni teh siunn7 e5 tiong-kan, lui5 koh tit8-tit8 tan5, chit e5 si5-chun7 Gi7-sin3 tann bo5 kio3 ma-ma, si7 hoan2-tng2 kio3 Siong7-te3 kong2, Goa2 m7-kann2 koh tham-sim, kiu5 Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 i, i beh chiong chiah e5 chinn5 theh8 tng2-khi3 heng5 i e5 peng5-iu2.
Sio2 peng5-iu2 Siong7-te3 moa2 u7 lin5-bin2 thiann3-sioh I sou2 chhong3-cho7 e5 lang5; chiu7 hou7 lui5 tiam7-khi3, hong ia7 bo5 hiah nih8 teh thau3, Gi7-sin3 chiu7 khi2-lai5 bak8-sai2 cho3 chui2 bin7 chhit-chhit le3, chiu7 oat8-to3-tng2 khi3 hak8-hau7, kau3 hak8-hau7 mng5, ti7 chiann3-chhiu2-peng5 e5 chhau2-pou, khoann3-kinn3 i e5 peng5-iu2 chiong chheh-pau lai7 e5 mih8 kap chheh long2 to3 ti7 chhau2-pou tit8-tit8 teh peng2 teh chhoe7, i chiu7 kiann5 oa2-khi3 ka7 i kio3, To7-jin5 li2 teh chhoe7 sim2-mih8, i in3 i kong2, Goan2 ma-ma tui3 chhu3-pinn chioh 20 khou beh hou7 goa2 kau chheh-chinn5, goa2 ki3-tit khng3 ti7 chit-chan3 se3-chan3 e5 lai7-bin7 e5 te7-a2 lai7, tann chit-chun7 beh theh8 khi3 kau soa3 theh8 bo5, sou2-i2 chiong te7-a2 lai7 e5 mih8 long2 to3 chhut-lai5 teh chhoe7.
Gi7-sin3 khu5 loh8-khi3 tui3 To7-jin5 e5 chhiu2 ka7 khan-le3, tit8-tit8 hau2, To7-jin5 mng7 i li2 teh hau2 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3 li2 e5 ia7 phah m7-kinn3 si7 m7-si7?
Gi7-sin3 ka7 To7-jin5 kong2, To7-jin5 chhiann2 li2 sia3-bian2 goa2 ho2 m7-ho2, chiu7 chiong 20 khou khng3 ti7 To7-jin5 e5 chhiu2, To7-jin5 chin hoann-hi2, m7-si7 hoann-hi2 20 khou chhoe7-tioh8, si7 hoann-hi2 Gi7-sin3 e5 hoan2-hoe2, in-ui7 Gi7-sin3 si7 chit8 e5 chin gau5 thau-theh8 e5, koh m7 thak8-chheh, in ma-ma siong5-siong5 ka7 i kong3, ia7 m7 hoan2-hoe2, kin-a2-jit8 chainn2-iunn7 beh hoan2-hoe2, chiu7 mng7 Gi7-sin3 kong2 chinn5 li2 ka7 goa2 theh8 khi3, a2-si7 khioh-tioh8; Gi7-sin3 ka7 i kong2 si7 ti7 li2 e5 chheh-pau lai7 theh8 khi3 e5, To7-jin5 ka7 i kong2 chin kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, li2 u7 hoan2-hoe2, Siong7-te3 si7 lin5-bin2 e5 Siong7-te3, ti7 i sou2 chhong3-cho7 it-chhe3 e5 oah8-mia7, Siong7-te3 long2 thiann3-thang3 po2-sioh i, an2-ni chin ho2, tann goa2 beh ka7 li2 e5 ma-ma kong2, in-ui7 li2 u7 hoan2-hoe2 Siong7-te3 u7 lin5-bin2 li2, khoann3-kou3 li2, tann lan2 tioh8 tak8 le2-pai3 lai5-khi3 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8, Siong7-te3 chiu7 beh ke3-siok8 thiann3 li2. (Sann-kap lai5 liam7 kim-ku3) (Ang5 Siok-kheng)
