Kim-ku3: Ia5-ho5-hoa u7 un-hui7, u7 lin5-bin2, bo5 khoai3-khoai3 siu7-khi3, toa7-toa7 u7 chu5-ai3. (Si-phian 145: 8)
Sio2 peng5-iu2, lin2 bat siunn7 kong2 goa2 sou2 bo5 ai3 e5 lang5 pat8 lang5 ia7 bo5 ai3 i a2 m7-bat? Koh lin2 bat siunn7 kong2 goa2 sou2 oan3-hun7 e5 lang5, ng3-bang7 u7 pat8-lang5 oe7 ka7 phah, a2-si7 khoann3 Siong7-te3 oe7 ka7 heng5-hoat8, hou7 i tu2-tioh8 kan-khou2 a2 m7-bat? Sui-jian5 lan2 siunn7 an2-ni, iau2-ku2 jit8-thau5 ia7-si7 teh chio3 in, hou7 in u7 sio-lo7. Ti7 chin joah8 e5 si5 lan2 siunn7 kong2 oe7 hou7 lan2 liang5-khoai3 e5 sai-pak hou7 kan-ta loh8 ti7 lan2 chia, mai3 loh8 tui3 goa2 sou2 oan3-hun7, tho2-iam3 e5 lang5 hia, chong2-si7 sai-pak hou7 ma7 si7 bo5 hun-piat8 sim2-mih8 lang5 teh loh8, chhin-chhiunn7 an2-ni thinn-te7 chu7-jian5 kai3 bo5 koan-he7 lang5 e5 kam2-cheng5, penn5-penn5 su3 un-hui7 hou7 lang5. siong7-te3 tui3 ban7-lang5 ia7 long2-si7 an2-ni peng5-teng2 e5 siunn2-su3 un-hui7. Chit e5 toa7 e5 chin-li2 chin oh-tit beng5-pek8, chong2-si7 Ia5-sou u7 ka7 lan2 kong2-beng5. Kou2-cha2 Iok-na2 ia7 boe7 beng5-pek8 chit e5 su7, au7-lai5 Siong7-te3 eng7 hoat-tou7 hou7 i beng5-pek8. Lan2 kin-a2-jit8 beh lai5 thiann chit e5 kou3-su7.
1. Cheng5 le2-pai3 koan-he7 Iok-na2 e5 kou3-su7 kong2 kau3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7? (toa7-hi5 thou3 Iok-na2 ti7 ta-te7) Tioh8, tai7-ke chin ho2 ki3-ti5. Tann Iok-na2 hou7 toa7-hi5 thou3 ti7 liok8-te7 liau2-au7, Siong7-te3 te7-ji7 pai2 tui3 Iok-na2 kong2 khi2--lai5, khi3 Ni5-ni5-bi5 hit e5 toa7-siann5, goa2 sou2 beng7-leng7 li2 thoan5--e5, li2 thoan5 hou7 i. Chit pai2 Iok-na2 sui5-si5 khi3 lah.
2. Iok-na2 chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, lai5 kau3 Ni5-ni5-bi5 siann5, chiu7 kiann5 tang phau2 sai, soan-thoan5 kong2 koh si3-chap8-jit8 Ni5-ni5-bi5 beh to2-hoai7, che si7 Siong7-te3 tui3 chit e5 pai7-hoai7 e5 siann5 e5 sin3-sek.
Ni5-ni5-bi5 siann5 e5 peh-sinn3 khoann3 chhut in kong-ngi7 e5 sim kap chan5-jim2 e5 sou2 cho3, u7 toa7-toa7 tek-choe7 Siong7-te3, chong2-si7 in u7 chit8 e5 ng3-bang7, kiam2-chhai2 Siong7-te3 hoe5-sim tng2-i3, ban2-hoe5 I e5 toa7 siu7-khi3, hou7 lan2 bo5 biat8 bo5 ia7 kann2. Tui3 an2-ni teng2 kau3 ti7 ong5-kiong e5 ong5, e7 kau3 cheng-sinn, choan5-pou7 kim3-chiah8, ong5 thng3 i e5 tiau5-hok8, tui3 po2-cho7 loh8--lai5, chheng7 moa5-sann che7 ti7 hoe2-hu teng2, piau2-si7 in-ui7 sou2 hoan7 e5 choe7 iu-siong. I beng7-leng7 kong2 lang5, cheng-sinn ia7 long2 m7-thang chiah8, m7-thang lim, ......long2 tioh8 chheng7 moa5, toa7 siann kiu5-kio3 Siong7-te3, tak8-lang5 li7-khui i e5 phainn2 lou7. Sou2 u7 e5 lang5 long2 khiam-pi, ai-khau3, ki5-kiu5 Siong7-te3. Tui3 an2-ni Siong7-te3 chiu7 bo5 kang3 chai-e7.
3. Iok-na2 chainn2-iunn7 nih? I m7-si7 chhin-chhiunn7 Siong7-te3 chit khoan2 thiann3 lang5. I khoann3 in hoe2-kai2, Siong7-te3 sia3-bian2 in lai5 bo5 hoann-hi2, i siunn7 Ni5-ni5-bi5 na7 chiau3 i sou2 kong2 biat8-bong5 m7 chin ho2, na7 an2-ni goan2 Iu5-thai3 kok chiu7 m7-bian2 koh hou7 in ap-pek. Chong2-si7 in hoan2-hoe2 bian2 biat8-bong5 lah, Iok-na2 hui-siong5 e5 m7-goan7, i cho7 chit8-keng liau5-a2 lai5 siam2 jit8 ai3 beh khoann3 hit e5 siann5 chainn2-iunn7. Chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 ti7 i e5 liau5-a2 pinn hou7 hoat chit8-chang5 pi-moa5 chin toa7 chang5, thang cho3 im3-ng2 hou7 Iok-na2 chin song2-khoai3, chong2-si7 Iok-na2 ia7 boe7 li2-kai2, sou2-i2 Siong7-te3 chiu7 hou7 thang5 lai5 ka7 hit chang5, hou7 ta lah khi3. Iok-na2 ui7-tioh8 hit chang5 chin bo5 chhai2. Ti7 chia Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 lim5-kau3 i kong2, 4 chiunn 10, 11 chat. Iok-na2 boe7-thang bo5 hok8-chiong5 Siong7-te3.
Lan2 tioh8 chhin-chhiunn7 Ia5-sou ka3-si7 lan2, lian5 lan2 e5 tui3-tek8 ia7 tioh8 thiann3 in, the3 in ki5-to2. (T. H. C.)
9 Geh8 20 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Tioh8 chiau3 chin-sit8 e5 kong-peng5 lai5 sim2-phoann3, tai7-ke eng7 chu5-ai3 lin5-bin2 lai5 sann khoan2-thai7. (Sat-ka-li7-a 7: 9)
Lan2 cha2-khi2 beh lai5 kong2 chit8 e5 sian-ti mia5 Sat-ka-li7-a, i u7 thoe3 Siong7-te3 kong2 oe7, chiu7-si7 eng3-un2 siu7-lan7 e5 I2-sek-liat8 peh-sinn3, in na7 hoan2-hoe2 hoe5-thau5 lai5 chhoe7-kiu5 Siong7-te3, Siong7-te3 tek-khak beh eng3-un2 in tit-tioh8 peng5-an, chit si5 goa2 beh eng7 chit8 e5 kou3-su7 lai5 piau2-hian7 chit e5 ka3-si7.
Cha2 ti7 bou2 siann5 u7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 kio3 choe3 Bi2-le7, Bi2-le7 pun2 m7 si7 siann5-lai7 ke-chhi7 e5 lang5, i si7 soann lai7 phian-phiah e5 soann-li2-lang5, in tau san3-hiong, chhu3-nih8 u7 pe7-bo2, i bat u7 chit8 e5 a-hiann, chong2-si7 ti7 Bi2-le7 5 hoe3 e5 si5 hiann-ko chiu7 si2-khi3. Tann pe7-bo2 chi2-u7 chhun i chit8 e5 kiann2 na7-tiann7, pe7-bo2 chin thiann3 i. In pa-pa teh chho3-chha5 tann khi3 ke-nih8 be7. Tui3 an2-ni thang tiah8-bi2, be2 chhai3 to3-lai5 tou7-oah8. Kau3 chap8-goa7 hoe3 e5 si5 i ia7 pang-chan7 pa-pa tau3 khioh-chha5, chong2-si7 i iau2 boe7 u7 lat8 thang tann chha5, kiann5 hiah-hng7 e5 soann-lou7, sou2-i2 i long2 m7-bat kau3 siann5-nih8 khi3 khoann3-khoann3. Chong2-si7 kau3 i 15 hoe3 e5 si5 pa-pa chiu7 ui7-tioh8 i be2 che7-che7 le2-mih8, u7 sui2-sann, sui2-e5, sui2-sui2 e5 hou7-soann3 to3-lai5 hou7 i. Tui3 an2-ni i chiu7 siunn7 siann5-nih8 tou-chhi7 un2-tang3 si7 chin lau7-jiat8, un2-tang3 iau2 u7 koh-khah sui2 e5 mih8, i chin ai3 khi3 khoann3-khoann3.
U7 chit8-jit8 si7 i 18 hoe3 ni5-thau5 i chiu7 kap a-pa tann chha5 chhut-khi3 siann5-nih8 be7, kau3-ui7 chit8-e7 khoann3, ko2-jian5 hou7 i e5 sim chin thang kiann, chin ki5-inn7, i bo5 phah-sng3 tou-chhi7 e5 seng-oah8 si7 kau3 hiah chhia-hoa5. I khoann3-kinn3 toa7-chhu3 koan5-lau5, khi3-chhia, tian7-teng, hi3-inn7, chiu2-lau5 bu5-ki5 put-iu2, ia7 khoann3-kinn3 che7-che7 lu2-chu2 chheng7 khi2 liu5-heng5 e5 i-hok8 kap koan5-kiah8-a2-e5. Hit e5 tann2-pan7 chiu7 tin2-tang7 i e5 sim, put-ti put-kak hou7 i senn-khi2 him-soan7 e5 sim.
Kau3 to3-khi3 i chiu7 tui3 pe7-bo2 tho2, kong2 i ai3 kau3 tou-chhi7 lai5 chhoe7 thau5-lou7. I e5 pe7-bo2 ka7 i kong2, li2 ni5-ki2 iau2 chio2 na7 siu7 be5-hek8 hit e5 tui7-loh8 chiu7 m7-si7 sio2-khoa2. Na7-si7 i m7-thiann, u7 chit8-jit8 seng7 i khi3 soann-nih8 beh chho3-chha5 e5 ki-hoe7, keng3-jian5 thau-chau2, kau3 i sou2 him-bou7 e5 tou-chhi7. Na7-si7 kau3-ui7, bo5 chhin-chhek, bo5 peng5-iu2, tann beh khi3 chhoe7 chi7-chui7? Ti7 ke-lou7 teh tong7-lai5 tong7-khi3, hut-jian5 khi3 tu2-tioh8 cheng5 bat siong5-siong5 ka7 i be2 chha5 e5 thau5-ke-niu5, chiu7 kap i khi3 in tau chiam7-si5 lai5 pang-bang5 chu2-chiah8. Na7-si7 sim cho-cho siunn7 ai3 tit-tioh8 khah liu5-heng5 e5 chng-thann7, him-bou7 sui2-sann, sui2-e5.
U7 chit8-jit8 thau5-ke-niu5 bo5 ti7-teh, hut-jian5 soa3 sann-khi2 tham-sim, soa3 ka7 thau5-ke-niu5 thau-theh8 chinn5. Tui3 an2-ni chau2-chhut thau5-ke-niu5 e5 chhu3, ko2-jian5 khi3 be2 e5, be2 sui2-sann, chheng7 khi2--lai5 giam2-jian5 si7 hu3-hou7 e5 chhian-kim sio2-chia2. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 kiat-kau phainn2 peng5-iu2, soa3 tui7-loh8 kau3 ti7 ian-hoa chiu2-koan2, thiau3-bu2-tiunn5, ui7-tioh8 i e5 sui2 kap sun5-cheng5, chiu7 tit-tioh8 che7-che7 lam5 peng5-iu2. Na7-si7 choe7 e5 kang-chinn5, eng-kai siu7 e5 heng5-hoat8 kau3 lah, chiu7-si7 cheng5 hou7 i thau-theh8 e5 thau5-ke-niu5 khi3 po3 kiann, keng2-chhat put-si5 teh tui-chhoe7, keng2-jian5 hou7 lang5 chhoe7 tioh8 lah, koh hoat-kak i si7 chit8 e5 bo5 siu7 hu2-kho2 e5 si7-eng3-seng, ki5-sit8 i i2-keng poann5-koe3 si7-eng3-seng e5 seng-oah8, i2-keng si7 chit8 e5 am3-chinn7 e5 chhiong-ki.
Bian2 loa7-ku2 i chiu7 siu7 koainn ti7 kann-gak8. Tng i 20 hoe3 e5 ni5-boe2 penn7 to2 ti7 kann-gak8 lai7 chit8-keng se3-se3 e5 kann-pang5 e5 penn7-chhng5 teng2, kau3 hit si5 i chiu7 siunn7 tioh8 chhu3-nih8 e5 pe7-bo2 lah. Siunn7 kinn3 i choe3 se3-kiann2 ti7 chhu3-nih8, sui-jian5 ti7 soann-nih8 e5 seng-oah8, iau2-ku2 ti7 pe7-bo2 thiann3 e5 e7-bin7 kap ti7 soann-nih8 hit khoan2 chheng-cheng7, sun5-kiat e5 seng-oah8 si7 ho5-teng2 e5 hok-khi3, ho5-teng2 e5 khoai3-lok8 kap peng5-an.
Tann lai5 kong2 in chhu3, i e5 pe7-bo2 tui3 Bi2-le7 chhut-khi3 liau2-au7 hui-siong5 e5 iu-bun7. Chhun nng7 e5 hu-hu7 kui2-pai2 kam2-kak oah8 teh bo5 chhai2-kang, siunn7 beh si2, kai-chai3 ti7 chit8 e5 bo5 phah-sng3 e5 ki-hoe7 in chiu7 tit-tioh8 Chu2 e5 hok-im. Tui3 an2-ni in chiu7 lai5 pai3 Siong7-te3, nng7 e5 hu-hu7 chin jiat8-sim ui7-tioh8 chit e5 cha-bou2-kiann2 lai5 ki5-to2, chhim-sin3 Siong7-te3 beh sia3-bian2, beh chin2-kiu3, beh eng3-un2 kinn3-na7 sin3 I koh chin-chiann3 hoe2-kai2 e5 lang5 tit-tioh8 chin e5 peng5-an. U7 chit8-jit8 ti7 chit8 e5 tek8-piat8 e5 chip8-hoe7, bo5 phah-sng3 cheng5 choe3 Bi2-le7 e5 thau5-ke-niu5 e5 chi2-moai7 ia7 lai5 thiann to7-li2.
Tu7 ki5-to2 tiong chiah chai chit e5 su7, tui3 an2-ni thau5-ke-niu5 chiu7 chhoa7 in nng7 e5 hu-hu7 khi3 tham3-kann, khi3 e5 si5 Bi2-le7 to2 ti7 chhng5-nih8 sin-the2 chin loan2-jiok8, khoann3 tioh8 pe7-bo2 lai5 sim chin kam2-kek, khui-siann hau2 pe7-bo2 ia7 hau2, Bi2-le7 ia7 khoann3 thau5-ke-niu5 lai5, chin kian3-siau3 chhim-chhim jin7-choe7, pe7-bo2 thoe3 i ki5-to2, ia7 khou2-khng3 i chiap-siu7 Ia5-sou. Bi2-le7 chiu7 chhim-chhim tui3 Chu2 jin7-choe7, sim-lai7 ko2-jian5 tit-tioh8 toa7 peng5-an, kai-chai3 koh bian2 loa7-ku2 heng5-ki5 moa2, chiu7 siu7 thau2-pang3. Hit si5 i e5 lau7-pe7 lai5 chiap i to3 khi3 chhu3-nih8, kau3 hit si5 i chiah thong3-kam2 hoe5-thau5 ti7 pe7-bo2 e5 sin-pinn e5 hok-khi3. Siong7-te3 e5 peh-sinn3 ia7-si7 chhin-chhiunn7 an2-ni, Siong7-te3 u7 eng3-un2 chin e5 peng5-an beh hou7 lang5, na7-si7 teh ng3-bang7 lang5 hoan2-hoe2, hoe5-thau5 lai5 kiann5 I e5 ka3-si7.
9 Geh8 27 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Lang5 khoann3 goa7-mau7, Ia5-ho5-hoa si7 khoann3 sim-lai7. (I Sat-bo2-jinn2 16: 7)
Thian-su3-chim2 si7 chit8-ui7 jiat8-sim pai3 Siong7-te3 e5 lang5, i u7 3 e5 hau7-senn long2 chin koai koh gau5 thak8-chheh, chhu3-pinn e5 lang5 long2 chin o-lo2, ma-ma chin hoann-hi2, u7 chit8-jit8 ma-ma beh chhut-goa7 khi3 tham3 chhin-chiann5, kau-tai3 3 e5 hau7-senn kou3-chhu3, 3 lang5 long2 bo5 chha2 beh toe3 ma-ma khi3, ma-ma chiu7 an-sim chhut-goa7, chit 3 e5 hiann-ti7 siunn7 che7-che7 hoat-tou7 ng3-bang7 ma-ma tng2-lai5 e5 si5 e7 hoann-hi2 in. Toa7-kiann2 piau2-beng5 i u7 thiann3 ma-ma, chiu7 cheng2-li2 ma-ma e5 pang5-keng kau3 chin chheng-khi3, te7 2 e5 kiann2 ti7 hoe-hng5 ban2 chin che7 hoe, chhah ti7 hoe-kan, beh hou7 ma-ma phinn7-phang khoann3-sui2.
Na7-si7 te7 3 e5 kiann2 long2 bo5 choe3 sim2-mih8, chi2-u7 sim siau3-liam7 ma-ma, kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 i peng5-an tng2-lai5, ma-ma tng2-lai5 e5 si5 toa7-kiann2 po3-ko3 cheng2-li2 pang5-keng, te7-ji7 e5 theh8 hoe-kan chhah-hoe lai5 hou7 ma-ma, ma-ma to chin hoann-hi2, chong2-si7 te7-sann e5 kiann2 lai5 ka7 ma-ma kong2, Ma-ma li2 chhut-goa7, goa2 e5 sim ia7 kap li2 chhut-goa7, goa2 tak8-me5 long2 chin siau3-liam7 li2 koann2-kin2 tng2-lai5, ia7 kiu5 Siong7-te3 po2-hou7 li2 peng5-an tng2-lai5. Ma-ma thiann-tioh8 an2-ni chiu7 pho7 i lai5 chim, ia7 lau5 hoann-hi2 e5 bak8-sai2.
Chit 3 e5 kiann2 long2 hou7 ma-ma hoann-hi2 chong2-si7 te7-sann e5 kiann2 sui-jian5 bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 piau2-hian7, iau2-ku2 i e5 lai7-sim e5 liam7-thau5 hou7 i e5 ma-ma te7-it hoann-hi2. Sio2 peng5-iu2! Siong7-te3 tui3 lan2 ia7-si7 an2-ni, I si7 khoann3-kau3 lan2 e5 lai7-sim, sou2-i2 si-jin5 an2-ni kong2:
Siong7-te3 ah, kiu5 Li2 kam3-chhat goa2, <BR>Chai goa2 e5 sim-su, <BR>Chhi3-giam7 goa2, chai goa2 e5 i3-su3, <BR>Khoann3 goa2 lai7-bin7 u7 sim2-mih8 phainn2 sou2 kiann5 a2-bo5.
Lan2 bo5-lun7 ho2 a2-si7 phainn2, lan2 e5 sim-lai7 e5 liam7-thau5 Siong7-te3 long2 khoann3 e7 chhut, chhiann2 lan2 tioh8 siong5-siong5 kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 lan2 e5 lai7-sim put-si5 chheng-khi3 hou7 Chu2 khoann3-kinn3 lai5 hoann-hi2. (I. L. Chhi5)
